hadiths[145]{hadithnumber,text}:
534,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pakeezgi nisf eman hai. (alhamdulillah) taraazu ko bhar deta hai. (subhanallah) aur (al-hamdulillah) aasmanon se zamin tak ki wusat ko bhar detey hain. Namaz noor hai. sadqa daleel hai. sabr roshni hai. Quran tumharey haq mein ya tumharey khilaf hujjat hai har insan din ka shuruat karta hai to (kuchh aamaal ke badley) apna saudaa karta hai, phir ya to khud ko aazad karne wala hota hai ya khud ko tabah karne waalaa."
535,abu-Awana ne Samak-bin-Harab se unhon-ne Musab-bin-Sad se riwayat ki ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ibne- Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas unki iyaadat ke liye gaey wo bimar they ibne-aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kya aap mere liye Allah se dua karengey unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Namaz pakeezgi ke baghair qabool nahi hoti aur sadqa naajaaiz tareeqey se hasil kiye huey maal se qabool nahi hota aur aap Basra ke Hakim reh chukey hain (kahin aisa na ho ke aap ke paas koi aisa maal aa gaya ho.)
536,"Shoba, Zayda aur Israel sab ne Samak-bin-Harab se usi asnaad ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki hai."
537,"Wahab-bin-Munabba ke bhai Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye wo hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hamein sunaiin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadison ka tazkira kya, unmein se ye bhi thi : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jab koi be wuzu ho jaey, to uski Namaz qabool nahi hoti yahan tak ke wuzu kare."
538,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Ata-bin-Yazeed ne unhein khabar di ke Humran ne, jo Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam hain, unhein bataya ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu ke liye pani mangwaya aur wuzu kya to donon hathon ko teen baar dhoya, phir kulli ki aur) naak mein pani daal kar) naak jhaadii, phir teen baar chehra dhoya, phir teen baar dayan bazu kohniyon tak dhoya, phir isi tarah bayan dhoya , phir apne sar ka masah kya, phir teen baar apna dayan paon takhnon tak dhoya , phir isi tarah bayan paon dhoya, phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aap ne isi tarah wuzu kya jis tarah maine ab kya hai, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne mere is wuzu ki tarah wuzu kya, phir uth kar do rakatein ada kin, un donon ke doran mein apne aap se baatein na kin, iske guzishta gunah maaf kar diye jaengey. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : hamarey ulma (taabea'iin) kaha kartey they ke ye kaamil tareen wuzu hai jo koi insan Namaz ke liye karta hai."
539,"Yaqoob ke walid Ibrahim (bin Sad) ne ibne-Shahab se baqi bachi sanad ke sath Humran se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhon-ne pani ka bartan mangwaya , phir apne hathon par teen baar pani undela aur unko dhoya , phir apna dayan hath bartan mein daala aur kulli ki aur) naak mein pani daal kar) naak jhaadi , phir teen baar apna chehra dhoya aur teen baar apne donon bazu kohniyon tak dhoey , phir sar ka masah kya, phir apne donon paon teen baar dhoey , phir kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne mere is wuzu ki tarah wuzu kya, phir 2 rakatein padhein jin mein (wo ( apne aap se baatein na kar raha tha, uske pichhley gunah maaf kar diye jaaengey."
540,"Jarir ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Humran se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo masjid ke aangan mein they aur Asr ke waqt unke paas muazzan aaya to unhon-ne wuzu ke liye pani mangaya , wuzu kiya, phir farmaya : Allah ki qasam! main tumhen aik hadis sunata hun, agar kitabullah ki aik aayat na hoti to main tumhen na sunata, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jo musalman wuzu karey aur achi tarah wuzu karey, phir Namaz padhey to iske wo gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain jo us Namaz aur agli Namaz ke darmyan hongey."
541,"Hisham se (Jareer ke bajaey) abu-Usaama, Wakee aur Sufiyan ki sanadon se bhi ye riwayat bayan ki gaee. unmein abu-Usama ki riwayat ke alfaz is tarah hain : achi tarah wuzu karey aur farz Namaz ada karey."
542,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : lekin Urwa, Humran ki taraf se hadis bayan kartey hain ke unhon-ne kaha : phir jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu kar liya to farmaya : Allah ki qasam! main tumhen aik hadis zaroor sunaaunga, Allah ki qism ! agar kitabullah ki aik aayat na hoti to main tumhen wo hadis na sunata : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jo aadmi wuzu karey aur wo achi tarah wuzu karey, phir Namaz padhey to uske wo gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain jo us Namaz aur agli Namaz ke darmyan hongey. Urwa ne kaha : wo aayat (jiski taraf Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne ishara kya) : bila shubah wo log jo un khuli nishaniyon aur hidayat ko chhipaatey hain jo ham ne utaariin, se lekar ( الّٰعِنُوْنَ ( tak hai."
543,"Ishaaq-bin-Saeed-bin-Amr-bin-Saeed-bin-Aas ne apne walid (Saeed-bin-Amr) se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Amr-bin-Saeed) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha, unhon-ne wuzu ka pani mangaya aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : koi musalman nahi jiski farz Namaz ka waqt ho jaey, phir wo uske liye achi tarah wuzu karey, achi tarah khushoo se usey ada karey aur achchey andaz se rukoo karey, magar wo Namaz uske pichhley gunahon ka kaffara hogi jab tak wo kabeera gunah nahi karta aur ye baat hamesha ke liye ki."
544,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Ahmad-bin-Abda zabi ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Humran se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas wuzu ka pani laya to unhon-ne wuzu kya, phir kaha : kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadisein bayan kartey hain jinki haqiqat main nahi janta magar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne mere us wuzu ki tarah wuzu kya, phir farmaya : jisne is tareeqey se wuzu kya iske pichhley gunah maaf ho gaey aur uski Namaz aur masjid ki taraf jana zyada (sawab ka kaam) hoga. ibne- Abda ki riwayat mein hai : main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhon-ne wuzu kya."
545,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : (is hadis ke alfaz Quteba aur Abu-Bakar ke hain) hamein Wakee ne Sufiyan ke hawale se abu-Nazar se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu Anas se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne maqaaid ke paas wuzu kya, kehney lagey : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wuzu (karke) na dikhaun? phir har uzu (ang) ko teen teen baar dhoya. Quteba ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya : Sufiyan ne kaha : abu-Nazar ne abu-Anas se riwayat bayan kartey huey kaha : un (Usman (rz)) ke paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kai log maujood they."
546,"Misar ne abu Sakhra Jame-bin-Shaddad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Humran-bin-Aban se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghusl aur wuzu ke liye pani rakha karta tha aur koi din aisa na aata ke wo thoda sa (pani) apne uper na baha letey ( halka sa ghusl na kar letey , aik din) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us Namaz se ( Misar ka qaul hai : mera khayal hai ke Asr ki Namaz murad hai) salam pherney ke baad ham se baat-cheet ki, aap ne farmaya : main nahi janta ke aik baat tum se keh dun ya khamosh rahun? ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! agar bhalai ki baat hai to hamein bata dijiye , agar kuchh aur hai to Allah aur uska rasool behtar jantey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo bhi musalman wuzu karta hai aur jo wuzu Allah ne uske liye farz qarar diya hai usko mukammal tareeqey se karta hai phir ye panchon namazein ada karta hai to yaqinan ye namazein un gunahon ka kaffara bin jaeyngi jo un namazon ke darmyan ke oqaat mein huey."
547,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne apne walid se aur Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashaar ne Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ghandar ( se riwayat ki, un donon ( Muaz aur ibne- Jafar ( ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne jaame ibne-Shaddad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Humran-bin-Aban se suna, wo Bashir ke doore-amaarat mein us masjid mein abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) ko bata rahe they ke Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne is tarah wuzu ko mukammal kya jis tarah Allah ne hukm diya hai to ( uski ( farz namazein un gunahon ke liye kaffara hongi jo unke darmyan sarzad huey. ye ibne-Muaaz ki riwayat hai, ghandar ki hadis mein Bishr ke daure-hukoomat aur farz namazon ka zikr nahi hai."
548,"Makhrima ke walid Bukair (bin-Abdullah) ne Humran (maulaa Usmaan) se riwayat ki ke aik din Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bahut achi tarah wuzu kya, phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne bahut achi tarah wuzu kiya, phir farmaya : jisne is tarah wuzu kya, phir masjid ki taraf nikla, Namaz hi ne usey (jaaney ke liye) khada kya to uske guzrey huey gunah maaf kar diye jaaengey."
549,"Muaz bin Abdur-Rehman ne Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Humran se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jisne Namaz ke liye wuzu kya aur wuzu ki takmeel ki, phir farz Namaz ke liye chal kar gaya aur logon ke sath ya jamat ke sath Namaz ada ki ya masjid mein Namaz padhi, Allah Taala uske gunah maaf kar dega."
550,Alaa ne apne walid Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panchon namazein aur (har) Juma (doosrey) Juma tak darmyani muddat ke gunahon ka kaffara (unko mitaaney waale) hain jab tak kabeera gunah na kiya jaaey.
551,"Muhammad (bin Sirin ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : panchon namazein aur aik Juma (doosrey ( Juma tak darmyani muddat ke gunahon ka kaffara hain."
552,"Umar-bin Ishaq ke walid Ishaq (bin-Abdullah) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : jab ( insan ( kabeera gunahon se bach raha ho to panch namaazein, aik Juma (doosrey ( Juma tak aur aik Ramazan doosrey Ramazan tak, darmyan ke waqt mein hone-waale gunahon ko mitaaney ka sabab hain."
553,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne Rabee bin Yazeed ke hawale se abu-Idrees Kholani se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Utba-bin- Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. isi tarah (Muaawiya ne) kaha : mujhey abu-Usmaan ne Jubair-bin-Nufair se, unhon-ne Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamarey zimmey oont charaney ka kaam tha, meri baari aaii, to main Sham ke waqt unko charaa kar wapas laya to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap khadey ho kar logon ko kuchh irshad farma rahe they, mujhey aap ki ye baat ( sunney ko) mili : jo bhi musalman wuzu karta hai aur wo achi tarah wuzu karta hai, phir khadey ho kar poori yaksooii aur tawajjoh ke sath 2 rakaat Namaz padhta hai to uske liye jannat wajib ho jati hai. maine kaha : kya khub baat hai ye ! to mere samney aik kehney wala kehney laga : is se pahley wali baat usse bhi zyada umda hai. maine dekha to wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) they, unhon-ne kaha : maine dekha hai tum abhi aaey ho, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is se pahley) farmaya tha : tum mein se jo shakhs bhi wuzu karey aur apne wuzu ko pura karey (ya khub achi tarah wuzu karey) phir ye kahey : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad uske bandey aur uske rasool hain, to uske liye jannat ke aathon darwazey khol diye jatey hain, jis se chahey dakhil ho jaaey."
554,"Zaid-bin-Hubab ne Muawiya-bin-Saleh se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iske baad pichhli riwayat ke alfaz hain, albatta unhon-ne (is tarah) kaha : jisne wuzu kya aur kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, wo akelaa hai, uska koi Sharik nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske bandey aur uske rasool hain."
555,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullaah-bin-Zaid-bin-Aasim Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki (unhein sharf sohbat hasil tha) , ( Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara ne) kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zaid se kaha gaya : hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ( sa ( wuzu karke dikhaaiin . is par unhon-ne pani ka aik bartan mangwaya , usey jhukaa kar usmein se apne donon hathon par pani undela aur unhein teen baar dhoya , phir apna hath daal kar pani nikala aur aik hi chullu kulli ki aur naak mein pani kheenchaa , ye teen baar kya, phir apna hath daal kar pani nikala aur apna chehra teen baar dhoya , phir apna hath daal kar pani nikala aur apne bazu kohniyon tak 2-2 baar dhoey , (taake ummat ko malum ho jaey ke kisi uzu (khaas ang) ko 2 baar dhona bhi jaaiz hai) phir hath daal kar pani nikala aur apne sar ka masah kya aur (aap ( apne donon hath ( sar par) aagey se peechhey ko aur peechhey se aagey ko laaey, (eik taraf masah karna aur usi hath ko dobara wapas lana mustahab hai) phir donon paon takhnon tak dhoey , phir kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wuzu isi tarah tha."
556,"( Khalid-bin Abdullah ke bajaey) Sulaimaan-bin-Bilaal ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa se baqi bachi hui pichhli sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki, us mein, takhnon tak, ke alfaz nahi hain."
557,"Malik-bin-Anas ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa ki sanad se yahi riwayat bayan ki aur kaha : unhon-ne teen baar kulli ki aur naak jhaadi . unhon-ne , aik hi chullu se, ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye aur, donon hath aagey se (peechhey ko) laey aur peechhey se (aagey ko) laaey, iske baad ye alfaz badhaatey : unhon-ne sar ke agley hissey se (masah) shuru kya aur donon hath guddi tak laaey, phir unko wapas karke usi jagah tak laey jahan se shuru kya tha aur apne donon paon dhoey."
558,"Behaz ne Wuhaib se aur us ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa se pichhli rawiyon ki asnaad ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : aur unhon-ne kulli ki, naak mein pani daala aur naak jhaadii, teen chullu pani se. aur ye bhi kaha : phir sar ka masah kya aur aagey se (peechhey ko) aur peechhey se (aagey ko) masah kya aik baar. Behaz ne kaha : Wuhaib ne ye hadis mujhey imlaa karaai aur Wuhaib ne kaha : Amr-bin-Yahyaa ne ye hadis mujhey 2 baar (2 mukhtalif mauqon par) imlaa karaaii."
559,"Haaroon-bin-Saeed eilii aur abu-Taahir ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Haris ne khabar di ke Hibbaan-bin-Waase' ne unhein hadis sunai (kaha : ( unke walid ne unse bayan kya (kaha : ( unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullaah-bin-Zaid-bin-Aasim Mazni Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne wuzu kya to kulli ki, phir naak jhaadii, phir teen baar apna chehra dhoya aur apna dayan hath teen baar aur doosra bhi teen baar dhoya aur sar ka masah us pani se kya jo hath mein bacha hua nahi tha aur apne paon dhoey yahan tak ke unko achi tarah saaf kar diya. (usi sanad ke aik rawi ( abu-Taahir ne hadis bayan kartey huey kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne Amr-bin-Haris se ye hadis sunai."
560,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf mansub kartey huey riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi kisi thos cheez ( patthar , dhila , toilet pepar wghaira) se istinja karey to taaq adad mein karey aur jab tum mein se koi wuzu karey to naak mein pani daaley, phir naak jhaadey."
561,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se manqul hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunaiin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye bhi thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi wuzu karey to donon nathnon se naak mein pani kheenchey phir naak jhaadey."
562,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Idrees Kholani se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo wuzu karey wo naak jhaadey aur jo istinja karey wo taaq adad (odd numbers) mein kare."
563,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Idrees Kholani ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) donon se suna keh rahe they : Rasulullah ne farmaya, . . . . . usi (pichhli hadis ki) tarah ."
564,"Esa-bin-Talha ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi neend se bedaar ho to teen baar naak jhaadey , shaitan uski naak ke baanson par raat guzaarta hai."
565,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs jab thos cheez se istinja karey to taaq adad (odd numbers) mein kare."
566,"Makhrima-bin-Bukair ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Shaddad ke aazad karda ghulam Salim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jis din Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan aaey aur unke paas wuzu kya to unhon-ne farmaya : Abdur-Rehmaan! khub achi tarah wuzu karo kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha : (wuzoo ke pani se tar na honey waali) eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai."
567,aik aur sanad se Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne Shaddaad-bin-Haad ke aazad karda ghulam abu Abdullah ( Salim ( se riwayat bayan ki ke wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur phir unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka uper zikr kya gaya farman naql kya.
568,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke Mehrii ke aazad karda ghulam Salim ne mujhey bataya ke main aur Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ke janazey ke liye nikley to ham Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey ke darwazey se guzrey ( wahan thahrey , wuzu ke liye Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) andar gaey. . . .) phir unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hawale se uper zikr ki gaee riwayat sunai."
569,"Nuaim-bin-abdullaah ne Shaddaad-bin-Haad ke aazad karda ghulam Salim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas tha. . . . phir us ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
570,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Hilaal-bin-Yasaaf se, unhon-ne abu-Yahya se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka se Madina wapas aaey. rastey mein jab ham aik pani ( wali manzil ( par pahunchey to Asr ke waqt kuchh logon ne jaldi ki, wuzu kya to jaldi mein they, ham un tak pahunchey to unki eidiyaan is tarah nazar aa rahi thin ke unhein pani nahi laga tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (aa kar) farmaya : (un ( eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai. wuzu achi tarah kya karo."
571,"Mansoor ke doosrey shagird Sufiyan aur Shoba ke hawale se bhi baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki gaee jis mein Shoba ne, khub achi tarah wuzu karo, ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye aur uski hadis (ki sanad) mein hai : abu-Yahya Aaraj se riwayat hai,"
572,"Yoosuf-bin-Maahik ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik safar ke doran main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se peechhey reh gaey, aap hamarey paas pahunchey to Asr ki Namaz ka waqt ho chuka tha, ham (main se kuchh log) apne paon par (jaldii mein) hath pherney lagey to aap ne buland awaz se farmaya : (un) eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai."
573,"Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko dekha jisne apni eidii nahi dhoi thi to aap ne farmaya : (un ( eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai."
574,"Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kuchh logon ko wuzu ke bartan se wuzu kartey dekha to kaha : wuzu achchhi tarah karo maine Hazrat abul-Qaasim ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : koonchon ke liye aag ka azab hai."
575,"Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : eidiyon ke liye aag ka azab hai"
576,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke aik shakhs ne wuzu kya to apne paon par aik naakhun jitni jagah chhod di, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko dekh liya aur farmaya : wapas jao aur apna wuzu khub achi tarah karo, wo wapas gaya, (hukm par amal kya) phir Namaz padhi."
577,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab aik Muslim (ya momin) banda wuzu karta hai aur apna chehra dhota hai to pani (ya pani ke aakhiri qatrey) ke sath iske chehrey se wo sarey gunaah, jinhein usne apni aankhon se dekhtey huey kya tha, khaarij ho jatey hain aur jab wo apne hath dhota hai to pani (ya pani ke aakhiri qatrey (ke sath wo sarey gunah , jo iske hathon ne pakad kar kiye they, khaarij ho jatey hain aur jab wo apne donon paon dhota hai to pani (ya pani ke aakhiri qatrey (ke sath wo tamam gunah , jo uske pairon ne chal kar kiye they, khaarij ho jatey hain yahan tak ke wo gunahon se paak ho kar nikalta hai."
578,"Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne wuzu kya aur khub achi tarah wuzu kya, to iske jism se iske gunah khaarij ho jatey hain yahan tak ke iske nakhunon ke nichey se bhi nikal jatey hain."
579,"Umara-bin-Ghaziya Ansari ne Nuaim-bin-Abdullah-Mujmir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko wuzu kartey dekha, unhon-ne apna chehra dhoya aur achi tarah wuzu kya, phir apna dayan bazu dhoya yahan tak ke uper bazu ki shuruaat tak pahunchey, phir apna bayan bazu dhoya yahan tak ke uper bazu ki shuruaat tak pahunchey, phir apne sar ka masah kya, phir apna dayan paanw dhoya yahan tak ke uper pindlii ki shuruaat tak pahunchey, phir apna bayan paanw dhoya yahan tak ke uper pindlii ki shuruaat tak pahunchey, phir kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah wuzu kartey dekha, aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din achi tarah wuzu karne ki wjah se tum log hi roshan chehron aur safaid chamakdaar hath paanw waley hogey, lihaza tum mein se jo apne chehrey aur hath paon ki roshni aur safedi ko aagey tak badha sakey, badha ley."
580,"Saeed-bin-abi-Hilal ne Naeem bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko wuzu kartey huey dekha, unhon-ne apna chehra aur bazu dhoey yahan tak ke kandhon ke qareeb pahunch gaey, phir unhon-ne apne paanw dhoey, yahan tak ke uper pindliyon tak le gaey, phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : meri ummat ke log qiyamat ke din wuzu ke asar se roshan chehron aur safaid chamakdaar hath paon ke sath aaeingey, lihaza tum mein se jo apni roshni ko aagey tak badha sakta hai, badha ley."
581,"Marwan ne abu-Malik Ashjai Sad-bin-Tariq se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mera hauz adn se iila tak ke faasley se zyada wasee hai aur) iska pani ( barf se zyada safaid aur shehad miley doodh se zyada sheereen hai aur uske bartan sitaron ki tadaad se zyada hain, (ye khaalisatan meri ummat ke liye hai, us liye) main ( ummat ke ilawa doosrey) logon ko us se rokoonga, jaisey aadmi apne hauz se logon ke oonton ko roktaa hai. sahaba kiram ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya us din aap hamein pahchaanengey? aap ne farmaya : haan, tumhari aik alamat hogi jo dusri kisi ummat ki nahi hogi, tum wuzu ke asar se chamaktey huey chehrey aur hath paanw ke sath mere paas aaogey."
582,"(Marwaan ke bajaey) ibne- Fuzel ne abu-Malik Ashjai se, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mere paas hauz par aaeygii aur main isi tarah (doosrey) logon ko us ( hauz ( se door hataaunga jaisey aik aadmi doosrey aadmi ke oonton ko apne oonton se hataataa hai. sahaba kiram ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kya aap hamein pahchaanengey? aap ne farmaya : haan, tumhari aik nishani hogi jo tumharey siwa kisi aur ki nahi hogi, tum mere paas wuzu ke asaraat se roshan chehrey aur chamakdaar haath-paanw ke sath aaogey. tum mein se aik giroh ko zabardastii mere paas aaney se rok diya jaeyga, to wo mujh tak nahi pahunch sakengey. is par main kahunga : aey mere rab! ye mere sathiyon mein se hain. aik farishta mujhey jawab dega aur kahega : kya aap jantey hain unhon-ne aap ke baad kya kya kaam eiijaad kiye they?"
583,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah mera hauz Eila se adn tak ke faasley se zyada wasee hai, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! main us se isi tarah (doosrey) logon ko hataaunga, jis tarah aadmi ajnabii oonton ko apne hauz se hataataa hai. sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aur kya aap hamein pehchan lengey? aap ne farmaya : haan, tum mere paas roshan chehrey aur chamaktey huey safaid haath-paanw ke sath aaogey, ye alamat tumharey siwa kisi aur main nahi hogii."
584,"Ismail (bin Jafar ( ne Alaa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabristaan mein aaey aur farmaya : aey eman wali qaum ke gharaaney! tum sab par salamati ho aur ham bhi insha-Allah tumharey sath milney waley hain, meri khahish hai ke ham ne apne bhaiyon ko (bhi) dekha hota. sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya ham aap ke bhai nahi? aap ne jawab diya : tum mere sathi ho aur hamarey bhai wo log hain jo abhi tak (duniyaa mein) nahi aaey. is par unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap apni ummat ke un logon ko, jo abhi (duniyaa mein) nahi aaey, kaisey pahchaaneingey? to aap ne farmaya : bataao! agar kaley siyah ghodon ke darmyan kisi ke safaid chehrey (aur ( safaid paon waley ghodey hon to kya wo apne ghodon ko nahi pahchaaney ga ? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi, aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : wo wuzu ki bina par roshan chehron , safaid hath paon ke sath aaeingey aur main hauz par unka pesh-rau hunga , khabardaar ! kuchh log yaqinan mere hauz se parey hataaey jaeinge , jaisey (kahiin aur ka ( bhatkaa hua oont (jo galey ka hissa nahi hotaa) parey hata diya jata hai, main unko awaz doonga, dekho! idhar aa jao. to kaha jaeyga unhon-ne aap ke baad (apne qaul w amal ko) badal liya tha. to main kahunga : door ho jao, door ho jao."
585,"Ismail ke bajaey Abdul-Azeez darawardi aur Malik ne Alaa se, unhon-ne apne walid Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabristaan ki taraf tashrif le gaey aur farmaya : aey eman wali qaum ke dayaar ! tum sab par salamati ho, ham bhi agar Allah ne chaha to tumharey sath milney waley hain. iske baad Ismail bin Jafar ki riwayat ki tarah hai. haan Malik ki riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : to kuchh logon ko mere hauz se hataya jaeyga (alaa) yani khabardaar ke bajaey (  ( , yani , to , ka lafz hai.)"
586,"abu-Hazim se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : main Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey khada tha aur wo Namaz ke liye wuzu kar rahe they, wo apna hath aagey badhaatey , yahan tak ke baghl tak pahunch jata, maine unse puchha : aey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ! ye kis tarah ka wuzu hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : aey Farukh ki aulad (aey bani Faaris ( ! tum yahan ho? agar mujhey pata hota ke tum log yahan khadey ho to main is tarah wuzu na karta. maine apne khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha : momin ka zewar wahan pahunchega jahan iske wuzu ka pani pahunchega."
587,"Ismail ne bayan kya ke unhein Alaa ne khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen aisi cheez se aagah na karun jiske zariey se Allah Taala gunah mitaa deta hai aur darjaat buland farmata hai? sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool kyon nahin! aap ne farmaya : naagawaariyon ke bawajud achi tarah wuzu karnaa, masaajid tak zyada qadam chalnaa, aik Namaz ke baad dusri Namaz ka intizar karnaa, so yahi (ribaat) (shaitaan ke khilaf jang ki chhaawnii) hai."
588,"(bajaaey Ismail ke) Malik aur Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, Shoba ki hadis mein, ribaat, ka tazkira nahi hai jabke Malik ki hadis mein 2 baar hai : yahi ribaat hai, yahi ribaat hai."
589,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar mujhey ye dar na hota ke main musalmanon ko (Zuhair ki riwayat mein hai : apni ummat ko) mashaqqat mein daal doonga to main unhein har Namaz ke waqt miswak karne ka hukm detaa.
590,"Misar ne Miqdaam-bin-Shureh se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se poochha, maine kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghar tashrif latey to kis baat ( kaam ( se shuruat farmatey they? unhon-ne farmaya : miswak se."
591,Sufiyan ne Miqdaam-bin-Shureh se baqi bachi hui pichhli sanad se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab apne ghar tashrif latey to miswak se shuruat farmatey.
592,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to miswak ka aik kinaaraa aap ki zaban par tha."
593,"Hushaim ne Husain se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko tahajjud ke liye khadey hotey to apna munh miswak se achi tarah saaf farmatey."
594,"Mansoor aur Aamash donon ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey . . . . . . aagey pichhli riwayat ki tarah hai lekin unhon-ne, tahajjud ke liye, ke alfaz riwayat nahi kiye."
595,Sufiyan ne Mansoor ke hawale se aur Husain aur Aamash ne (bhi Mansoor ki tarah) abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to apna munh miswak se achi tarah saaf farmatey.
596,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu mutawakkil ko bataya ke unhon-ne aik raat Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan guzari . Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke aakhiri hissey mein uthey, bahar nikley aur aasman par nazar dali phir Sura aale-Imraan ki aayat 190-191 tilaawat ki aur) فَقِنَا عَذَابَ النَّارِ ( tak pahunchey . phir ghar lautey aur achi tarah miswak ki aur wuzu farmaya, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhi, phir leit gaey, phir khadey huey, bahar aasman ki taraf dekha, phir ( dobara ( ye aayat padhi, phir wapas aaey, miswak ki aur wuzu farmaya, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhii."
597,"ibne-Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : fitrat (ke khasaayel) panch hain (ya panch cheezein fitrat ka hissa hain) : khatna karaanaa, naaf ke nichey baal moondnaa, naakhun taraashnaa, baghl ke baal ukhedna aur moonchh katarnaa."
598,"mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : ( khasaayel ( fitrat panch hain : khatna karaanaa , naaf ke nichey ke baal mundna , moonchh kutarnaa , naakhun tarashna aur baghl ke baal ukhednaa."
599,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : hamarey liye moonchhein katarney, naakhun taraashney, baghl ke baal ukhedney aur naaf ke nichey ke baal moondney ke liye waqt muqarrar kar diya gaya ke ham unko chalis (40) din se zyada na chhodein."
600,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : munchhein achi tarah taraasho aur daadhiyaan badhaao."
601,"Abu-Bakar bin Naafe ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) riwayat ki ke aap ne munchhein achi tarah taraashney aur dadhi badhaney ka hukm diya."
602,"Umar-bin Muhammad ne Naafe ke hawale se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mushrikon ki mukhalifat karo, munchhein achi tarah taraasho aur daadhiyaan badhaao."
603,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : munchhein achi tarah kaato aur daadhiyaan badhaao, majoos ki mukhalifat karo."
604,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Zakariiyaa-bin abi Zayda se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mus'ab-binSheba se, unhon-ne Talaq-bin-Habeeb se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : das cheezein ( khasaayel ( fitrat mein se hain : munchhein katarnaa, dadhi badhaanaa, miswak karnaa, naak mein pani kheenchnaa, naakhun taraashnaa, ungliyon ke jodon ko dhonaa, baghl ke baal ukhednaa, naaf ke nichey ke baal moondnaa, pani se istinja karna. Zakariya ne kaha : Musab ne bataya : dasween cheez main bhool gaya hun lekin wo kulli karna ho sakta hai. Quteba ne ye izafa kya ke Wakee ne kaha : (intiqaazul-maa) ke mana istinja karna hain."
605,"abu-Kuraib ne bayan kya, hamein abu Zayda ke betey ne apne walid (abu Zaayda) se khabar di, unhon-ne Mus'ab-bin-Sheba se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis riwayat ki, albatta ibne-abii-Zaayda ne kaha : unke walid ne kaha : main dasween baat bhool gaya hon."
606,Aamash ke 2 shagird Wakee aur abu-Muawiya ki sanadon se Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai (aur ye alfaz abu-Muawiya ke shaagirdii hai bin Yahya ke hain) ke un (salmaan (rz)) se (tanzan) kaha gaya : tumharey Nabi ne tum logon ko har cheez ki taleem di hai yahan tak ke qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) (ke tareeqey) ki bhii. kaha : unhon-ne jawab diya : haan (hamein sab kuchh sikhaya hai) aap ne hamein mana farmaya hai ham pakhaney ya peshab ke waqt qibley ki taraf rukh karein ya daaein hath se istinja karein ya istinjey mein teen pattharon se kam istemal karein ya ham gobar ya haddi se istinja karein.
607,"Aamash ke aik aur shagird Sufiyan ne unse aur Mansoor se, un donon ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mushrikon ne ham se kaha : main dekhta hun ke tumhara sathi (har cheez sikhaataa hai yahan tak ke tumhen qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ka tariqa bhi sikhaataa hai. to Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan, unhon hamein mana farmaya hai ke ham mein koi apne daaein hath se istinja karey ya qibley ki taraf munh karey aur aap ne hamein gobar aur haddi (se istinaa karne) se rokaa hai aur aap ne ye bhi farmaya hai : tum mein se koi teen pattharon se kam ke sath istinja na kare."
608,abu-Zubair ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein haddi ya leed ke zariey se istinja karne se mana farmaayaa.
609,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-Numair donon ne kaha, hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis sunai, neez Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis sunai (alfaz unhi ke hain) kaha : maine Sufiyan-bin-Uena se puchha : kya aap ne Zohri se suna ke unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Ayub se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki jagah par aao to na qibley ki taraf munh karo aur na uski taraf pusht karo, peshab karna ho ya pakhana , balke mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf munh kya karo. abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham Sham (Syria) gaey to ham ne baitul-khala qibla rukh baney huey paaey, ham us se rukh badaltey aur Allah se maafi talab kartey they? (Sufiyaan ne) kaha : haan."
610,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki jagah par baithey to na qibley ki taraf munh karey aur na hi uski taraf pusht kare."
611,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa se, unhon-ne apne chacha Waase'-bin-Hibbaan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main masjid mein Namaz padh raha tha aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apni pusht qibley ki taraf laga kar baithey huey they. jab maine apni Namaz poori kar li to apna pahlu badal kar unki taraf munh kar liya to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kuchh log kehtey hain : jab tum qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye baitho , jo bhi ho, qibley ki taraf aur baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke na baitho. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : halanke main ghar ki chhat par chadhaa to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke qazaey-hajat ke liye 2 enton par baitul-maqdis ki taraf rukh karke baithey huey they."
612,"Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Hibbaan apne chacha Waase'-bin-Hibbaan se aur wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhon-ne kaha : main apni behan (ummul-momeneen) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar (ki chhat ( par chadhaa to maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye baithey they, Sham (Syria) ki taraf rukh, qibley ki taraf pusht kiye huey."
613,"Hammam ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-abii-Qataada se, unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, abu Qatada ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi peshab kartey waqt uzu (ang) khas daaein hath mein na pakdey, na daaein hath se istinja karey aur na (paanii peetey waqt) bartan mein saans ley."
614,"Hisham dustwaai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada se, unhon-ne apne bap ( abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi baitul-khala mein dakhil ho to uzu (ang) khas apne daain hath se na chhuey."
615,"Ayub ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-abii-Qataada se, unhon-ne (apne waalid) Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke koi bartan mein saans ley ya apni sharm gaah ko apna dayan hath lagaey ya apne daain hath se istinja kare."
616,"abu-Ahwas ne Ashas se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab wuzu farmatey to wuzu mein, jab aap kanghi kartey to kanghi karne main aur jab aap jootaa pahntey to jootaa pahnney mein daain taraf se shuruat karna pasand farmatey they."
617,"Ashas ke aik doosrey shagird Shoba ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne tamam maamlaat mein, apne jootey pahnney, apni kanghi karne aur apne wuzu karne mein daain taraf se shuruaat karna pasand farmatey they."
618,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum 2 sakht laanat waley kaamon se bacho. sahaba kiram ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! sakht laanat waley wo 2 kaam kon se hain? aap ne farmaya : jo insan logon ki guzargaah mein ya unki saaya daar jagah main (jahaan wo aaraam kartey hain) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se faraghat) karta hai (log un donon kaamon par usko sakht bura bhala kehtey hain.)
619,"Khalid (Hazaa) ne Ataa-bin-abii-Memoona se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik ihaatey mein dakhil huey aur aap ke peechhey aik ladka bhi chala gaya jiske paas wuzu ka bartan tha, wo ham mein sabse chhota tha, us ne usey aik berii ke darakht ke paas rakh diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh huey) ki aur pani se istinja karke hamarey paas tashrif laey."
620,"2 mukhtalif sanadon se Shoba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Ataa-bin-abii-Memoona se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye khali jagah jatey to main aur mere jaisa aik ladka pani ka bartan aur aik neza uthatey (aur door tak aap ka sath detey (aur aap pani se istinja kartey."
621,"(Shoba ke bajaey) Rooh-bin-Qaasim ki sanad se Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye khuli jagah tashrif ley jatey to main aap ke liye pani ley jata, aap us se istinja kartey"
622,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim Nakhai se, unhon-ne Hammam se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Jarir ( bin-Abdullah Bajlii) (Raziallahu anhu) ne peshab kya, phir wuzu kya aur apne mozon par masah kya to unse kaha gaya : aap ye kartey hain? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne peshab kya, phir wuzu kya aur apne mozon par masah kya. Aamash ne kaha : Ibrahim ne bataya ke logon (ibne-Mas'ood (Raziallahu anhu) ke shaagirdon) ko ye hadis bahut pasand thi kyonke Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) sura Mayda ke nazil honey ke baad musalman huey they. ( sura Mayda mein aayat wuzu nazil hui thi aur aap ka ye amal iske baad ka tha jo aayat se mansukh nahi hua tha)"
623,"(abu-Muaawiya ke bajaey) Aamash ke doosrey bahut-sey shagirdon iisaa-bin-yoonus, Sufiyan aur ibne-Mus-hir ne bhi abu-Muawiya se hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, albatta Esa aur Sufiyan ki hadis mein hai, (Ibraaheem Nakhai ne) kaha : Abdullah (bin Masood (rz)) ke shagirdon ko ye hadis bahut pasand thi kyonke Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) sura Mayda ke utarney ke baad musalman huey they."
624,"Aamash ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha, aap aik khandan ke kodaa phainkney ki jagah par pahunchey aur khadey ho kar peshab kya to main door hat gaya. aap ne farmaya : qareeb aa jao. main qareeb ho kar (doosri taraf rukh karke) aap ke peechhey khada ho gaya ( faraghat ke baad) aap ne wuzu kya aur mozon par masah kya. ( qareeb khada karne ka maqsad uski ot lena tha. ("
625,"Mansoor ne abu-Waail ( Shaqiq ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) peshab ke barey mein sakhti kartey they aur botal mein peshab kartey they aur kehtey they : Bani-Israeel ke kisi aadmi ki jild par peshab lag jata to wo khaal ke itney hissey ko qainchi se kaat daalta tha. to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mera dil chahta hai ke tumhara sahib ( ustad ( is qadr sakhti na karey, main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) saath-saath chal rahe they, to aap diwar ke peechhey kodaa phainkney ki jagah par aaey, aap is tarah khadey ho gaey jis tarah tum mein se koi khada hota hai, phir aap peshab karne lagey to main aap se door ho gaya, aap ne mujhey ishara kya to main aa gaya aur aap ke peechhey khada ho gaya yahan tak ke aap farigh ho gaey."
626,Mughira-bin-Shoba se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah ‌(sl) apne kaam ko nikley in ki peechhey Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) pani ka dol lekar gaey aur aap jab haajat se farigh huey to pani daala aap par (yani wuzu ke waqt) phir wuzu kya aur masah kya mozon par. ‌ibne-Rumeh ki riwayat main yon hai pani daala aap par yahan tak ke aap farigh huey haajat se (yani wuzu se)
627,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ke aik doosrey shagird abdul-wahaab ne isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki aur kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna chehra aur donon hath dhoey , apne sar ka masah kya, phir mozon par masah kya."
628,"Aswad-bin-Halaal ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha aik raat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( sawari se) utrey aur qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas aaey to maine us bartan se jo mere paas tha, pani daalaa, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur apne mozon par masah kya."
629,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim (bin sabeeh Hamdani ( se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aik safar main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha, aap ne farmaya : aey Mughira ! pani ka bartan ley lo. maine bartan ley liya, phir aap ke sath niklaa. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chal padey yahan tak ke mujh se ojhal ho gaey, qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki, phir aap wapas aaey, aap ne tang aastinon wala shaami jubba pehna hua tha, aap uski aasteen se apna hath nikalney ki koshish karne lagey ( magar ( wo ( jubba ( tang ( Sabit ( hua. aap ne apna hath nichey se nikala , phir maine pani daala to aap ne Namaz jaisa wuzu farmaya, phir aap ne apne mozon par masah kya, phir Namaz padhi."
630,"Aamash se (abu-Muaawiya ke bajaey) iisaa-bin-yoonus) ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye nikley, jab wapas aaey to main pani ka bartan lekar aapko mila, maine pani daala , aap ne apne donon hath dhoey , phir chehra dhoya , phir hath dhoney lagey to jubba tang nikla, aap ne hath jubbey ke nichey se nikal liye, unko dhoya , sar ka masah kya aur apne mozon par masah kya, phir hamein Namaz padhai."
631,"Zakariya ne Aamir ( Shabi ( se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Mugheera ne apne walid Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : aik raat main safar ke doran mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha, aap ne puchha : kya tumharey paas pani hai? maine kaha : ji haan. to aap apni sawari se utrey, phir paidal chal diye yahan tak ke raat ki siyaahii mein ojhal ho gaey, phir ( wapas ( aaey to maine bartan se aap (ke hathon ( par pani daala , aap ne apna chehra dhoya (is waqt) aap oon ka jubba pahney huey they, aap usmein se apne hath na nikal sakey yahan tak ke donon hathon ko jubbey ke nichey se nikala aur kohniyon tak apne hath dhoey aur apne sar ka masah kya, phir maine aap ke mozey utaarney chahey to aap ne farmaya : unko chhodo, maine baa-wuzoo ho kar donon paon unmein daley they, aur un par masah farmaayaa."
632,"Aamir Shabi ke aik doosrey shagird Umar-bin-abi-Zayda ne Urwa-bin-Mugheera ke hawale se unke walid se riwayat ki ke unhon ( Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wuzu karaayaa, aap ne wuzu kya aur apne mozon par masah kya. Mughira ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (is barey mein) baat ki to aap ne farmaya : maine unhein baa-wuzoo haalat main ( mozon mein) dakhil kya thaa."
633,"Humaid Taweel ne kaha : hamein Bikar-bin-abdullaah-Muznii ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Mugheera-bin-Shoba se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (qaafley se) peechhey reh gaey aur main bhi aap ke sath peechhey reh gaya, jab aap ne qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se faraaghat) kar li to farmaya : kya tumharey sath pani hai? mein aap ke paas wuzu karne ka bartan laya , aap ne apne donon hath aur chehra dhoya, phir donon bazu kholney lagey to jubbey ki aasteen tang pad gaee, aap ne apna hath jubbey ke nichey se nikala aur jubba kandhon par daal liya, apne donon bazu dhoey aur apne sar ke agley hissey, pagdi aur mozon par masah kya, phir aap sawar huey aur main (bhi) sawar hua, ham logon ke paas pahunchey to wo Namaz ke liye khadey they, Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) unko Namaz padha rahe they aur aik rakaat padha chukey they. jab unhein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki tashrif aawrii) ka ehsas hua to peechhey hatney lagey. aap ne unhein ishara kya (ke Namaz poori karo) to unhon-ne Namaz padha di, jab unhon-ne salam phera to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey, mein bhi khada ho gaya aur ham ne wo rakaat padhi jo ham se pahley ho chuki thi."
634,"Umayya-bin-Bistaam aur Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne kaha : hamein Motamir ne apne walid se hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Bakr-bin-Abdullaah ne Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey ke waastey se Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mozon, apne sar ke samney ke hissey aur apne amaamey par masah farmaya,"
635,"Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne kaha : hamein Motamir ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Bakr se, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi riwayat bayan ki. ( Bakr ne Urwa-bin-Mugheera se Hasan ke hawale se bhi ye riwayat hasil ki aur seedhey-seedhey bhi suni. ("
636,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne (Sulaimaan ( Taimi se, unhon-ne Bakr-bin-Abdullaah se, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki (bakr ne kaha : maine Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se (bilaa-waasta bhi) sunaa) ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur apne sar ke agley hissey par aur pagdi par aur mozon par masah kya."
637,"abu-Muawiya aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Hakam se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Laila se, unhon-ne Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mozon par aur sar dhaanpney waley kapdey par masah kya. Esa ki hadis mein, Hakam se (riwaayat ki), aur, Bilal se riwayat ki, ke bajaey mujhey Hakam ne hadis sunai aur mujhey Bilal ne hadis sunai, ke alfaz hain."
638,aur yahi riwayat mujh (Imam muslim) ko Suwed-bin-Saeed ne Ali-bin-Mus-hir se aur unhon-ne Aamash se uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath bayan ki. usmein (yaqeenan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) ke bajaey (maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhaa) ke alfaz hain.
639,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan Sory ne Amr bin Qais mulaaii se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hakam bin utaibaa se, unhon-ne Qaasim-bin-Mukhaimira se, unhon-ne Shureh-bin-Haanii se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas mozon par masah ke barey mein poochhney ki gharaz se hazir hua to unhon-ne kaha : ibne-abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jao aur unse poochho kyonke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar kya kartey they. ham ne unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musaafir ke liye teen din aur teen raatein aur muqeem ke liye aik din aur aik raat (ka waqt) muqarrar farmaya, (Abdur-Razzaaq ne) kaha : Sufiyan ( Sory ( jab bhi Amr (bin Qais mulaaii) ka tazkira kartey to unki tareef kartey."
640,Zaid-bin-abii-Unaisaa ne hukm se mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
641,"Aamash ne Hakam ke hawale se Qaasim-bin-Mugheera se aur unhon-ne Shureh-bin-Haanii se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se mozon par masah ka masla puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jao kyonke wo us masley ko mujh se zyada jantey hain. to main Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi (jo uper mazkoor hai) ke mutabiq bayan kya."
642,"Sulaiman-bin-Barida ( Aslami ( ne apne walid se riwayat ki Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din kai namazein aik wuzu se padhein aur apne mozon par masah farmaya, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se puchha : aap ne aaj aisa kaam kya jo aap ne pahley kabhi nahi kya. aap ne jawab diya : umr ! maine jan-boojhkar aisa kya hai."
643,Abdullah-bin Shaqiq ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi apni neend se bedaar ho to us waqt tak apna hath bartan mein na daley jab tak usey teen baar dho na ley kyonke usey malum nahi hai ke raat ke waqt iska hath kahan ( kahan ( rahaa.
644,"Wakee aur abu-Muawiya ki sanadon se Aamash se riwayat hai, unhon-ne abu-Rizeen aur Abu-Saleh se aur un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki. abu-Muawiya ki riwayat mein hai : ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( jabke ( Wakee ki riwayat main ( hai) kaha : (aur ( usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf mansub kya. ( aagey ( usi (pichhli riwayat ( ki tarah hai."
645,"abu-Salma aur ibne-Musaiyab donon ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (mazkura (uper zikr) bir-Riwayat ( ki tarah baabiyaan kya."
646,Jaabir ( bin-Abdullah ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) ne un ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs neend se bedaar ho to ( wuzu ka pani nikalney ke liye) apne bartan mein hath dalney se pahley teen baar apne hath par pani daley (aur hath dhoey ( kyonke wo nahi janta iske hath ne kis ( haalat ( mein raat guzaarii.
647,"Aaraj , Muhammad , Alaa ke walid Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob , Hammam-bin-Munabba aur Saabit-bin-Ayaaz (sab ( ne kaha : hamein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, sabhii ne apni apni riwayat main ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis bayan ki. sabhii kehtey hain : yahan tak ke us ( hath ( ko dho ley , aur unmein se kisi ne bhi, , teen baar, ka lafz nahi bola, siwaey un riwayat ke jo ham ne uper Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) , ibne-Musaiyab , abu-Salma , Abdullah-bin Shaqiq , Abu-Saleh aur abu zarreen se bayan ki hain kyonke un sab ki hadison mein, teen baar, ka zikr hai."
648,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne hadis bayan ki ke hamein Aamash ne abu-Rizeen aur Abu-Saleh se khabar di, un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein kutta zaban ke sath pi ley to wo us cheez ko baha de, phir bartan ko saat (7) baar dho ley."
649,"Ismail bin Zakariya ne Aamash ke hawale se, baqi uper zikr ki gayi sanad ke saath, yahi riwayat bayan ki lekin, 'usey bahaa de' ke alfaz nahi kahey."
650,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab kutta tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein pi ley to wo usey saat (7) baar dhoey.
651,"Muhammad-bin Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumharey bartan mein se kutta pi ley to uski tahaarat (paakii) ye hai ke usey saat (7) baar dhoey, pehli baar mitti ke sath dhoey."
652,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunaaiin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye bhi thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ke bartan mein se kutta pi ley to uski pakeezgi ye hai ke usey saat (7) baar dhoey."
653,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne hamein apne walid se hadis bayan ki (kaha : ( hamein mere walid ne, unhein Shoba ne abu Tayyaah se riwayat kartey huey hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Mutrif-bin-Abdullaah se suna, ibne-mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kutton ko qatl karne ka hukm diya, phir farmaya : unka kutton se kya waasta hai? phir (logon se zarooriyaat ki tafseel sun kar) shikar aur bakriyon (ki hifazat karne) waley kuttey (rakhney) ki ijazat di aur farmaya : jab kutta bartan mein se pi ley to usey saat (7) martaba dho'o aur aathween baar (zyaada riwayat mein hai aik baar) mitti se saaf karo."
654,"( Khalid ( bin-Haaris , Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar , sab ne Shoba se isi sanad se us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta Yahya-bin-Saeed ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai ke aap ne bakriyon ki hifazat , shikar aur kheti ki rakhwaalii ke liye kutta rakhney ki ijazat di. Yahya ke siwa zara' ( kheti (ka zikr kisi riwayat mein nahi."
655,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey huey pani mein peshab karne se mana farmaya hai.
656,"Ibne-Sirin ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : tum se koi hargiz thehrey huey pani mein peshab na karey, phir usmein se nahaaey."
657,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kuchh hadison sunain unmein se aik ye thi : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khadey huey pani mein, jo chal na raha ho, peshab na karo ke phir tum usmein nahaao."
658,"Bukair-bin-Ashajj se riwayat hai ke Hishaam-bin-Zohra ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Saaib ne unhein hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi thahrey huey pani mein ghusle-janabat na kare. ( abu-Saaib ne) kaha : aey Abu-Hurera ! wo kya karey? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo (is mein se) pani ley ley."
659,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik badwi ne masjid mein peshab (karnaa shuru') kar diya, kuchh log uth kar uski taraf lapkey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey chhod do, usey (peshaab ke) darmyan mein mat roko. jab wo farigh ho gaya to aap ne pani ka dol mangwaya aur usey is par baha diya. (paanii ke sath wo peshab zamin ke andar chala gayaa.)"
660,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kar rahe they ke aik badwi masjid ke aik koney mein khada ho gaya aur wahan peshab karne laga, log is par chillaaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey chhod do. jab wo farigh hua to aap ne (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (pani ka ( aik bada dol laney ka hukm diya aur wo dol us ( peshab ( par baha diya gaya."
661,"Ishaq bin abi Talha ne riwayat ki, kaha : mujh se Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, wo Ishaq ke chacha they, kaha : ham masjid main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they ke us doran mein aik badwi aaya aur us ne khadey ho kar masjid mein peshab karna shuru kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ne kaha : kya kar rahe ho? kya kar rahe ho? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey ( darmyan mein) mat roko, usey chhod do. sahaba kiram ne usey chhod diya yahan tak ke usne peshab kar liya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur farmaya : ye masaajid is tarah peshab ya kisi aur gandagi ke liye nahi hain, ye to bas Allah Taala ke zikr Namaz aur tilawate-Quran ke liye hain. ya jo ( bhi) alfaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaai .) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir aap ne logon mein se aik ko hukm diya, wo pani ka dol laya aur usey is par baha diya."
662,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid (Urooj-bin-Zubair) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi (apni khaala) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bachchon ko laya jata tha, aap unke liye barkat ki dua farmatey aur unko ghuttii detey. aap ke paas aik bachcha laya gaya, us ne aap par peshab kar diya to aap ne pani mangwaya aur uske peshab par baha diya aur usey ( ragad kar) dhoya nahi."
663,"Jarir ne Hisham se riwayat ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik doodh peetaa bachcha laya gaya, us ne aap ki god mein peshab kar diya to aap ne pani mangwa kar is par baha diya."
664,Hisham ke aik aur shagird Esa ne Hisham ki isi sanad se ibne-Numair ki riwayat (662) ke mutabiq riwayat bayan ki aur kaha : aapney mangwaya aur usey chhidka.
665,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Qais binte- Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo apne bachchey ko, jisne abhi khana shuru na kya tha, lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur usey aap ki god mein daal diya to usne peshab kar diya, aap ne is par pani chhidakney se zyada kuchh na kya."
666,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath (oopar zikr ki gai) riwayat ki aur kaha : aap ne pani mangwaya aur usey chhidkaa.
667,"Yunus bin Yazeed ne kaha : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood ne Hazrat Umme- Qais-binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) se (wo jo sabse pahley hijrat karne wali un aurton mein se thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bait ki thi aur Ukaasha-bin-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) jo banu-Asad bin Khuzaima ke aik fard hain, ki behan thiin) riwayat ki, kaha : unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein apna betaa lekar hazir huin jo abhi us umr ko na pahuncha tha ke khana kha sakey. (ibne-Shahaab ke ustaad) Ubaidullah ne kaha : unhon (umme-Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ne mujhey bataya ke mere us betey ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki god mein peshab kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani mangwaya aur usey apne kapdey par baha diya aur usey achi tarah dhoya nahi."
668,"Khalid ne abu-Mashar se, unhon-ne Ibrahim Nakhai se, unhon-ne Alqama aur Aswad se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas thehra , subah ko wo apna kapda dho raha tha to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : terey liye kafi tha ke agar tu ney kuchh dekha tha to uski jagah ko dho deta aur agar tu ney isey nahi dekha to iske ird-gird ( tak) pani chhidak deta. maine apne aapko us haal mein dekha ke main usey ( madda manwiya ko) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se achi tarah khurachti thi, phir aap us kapdey mein Namaz padhtey they."
669,"Aamash ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad aur Hammam se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se maadda manwiya ke barey mein riwayat ki, kaha : main usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se khurch deti thi."
670,"(Khalid ki bajaey) abu-Mashar ke doosrey shagird Hisham-bin-Hasaan aur ibne-abi-Arooba ne Khalid ke ham mana riwayat ki. isi tarah Ibrahim Nakhai ke bahut-sey doosrey shagirdon Mugheera, Waasil ahadab aur Mansoor ne apni apni mukhtalif sanadon se Ibrahim Nakhai se, unhon-ne abu Aswad ke hawale se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se mani khurachney ki riwayat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se isi tarah bayan ki jis tarah Khalid ki abu Maashar se riwayat ( : 668 ( hai."
671,"ibne-Uena ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Hammam se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha se uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki."
672,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne Amr-bin-Memoon se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se aadmi ke kapdey ko lag janey wali mani ke barey mein puchha ke insan us jagah ko dhoey ya ( poorey ( kapdey ko dhoey ? to unhon ( Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ( ne kaha : mujhey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kapdey se) mani ko dhotey, phir usi kapdey mein Namaz ke liye tashrif ley jatey aur main usmein dhoney ka nishan dekh rahi hoti."
673,"abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad , ibne-Mubarak aur ibne-abi-Zayda ne Amr-bin-Memoon se pichhli sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki, albatta ibne-abi-Zayda ki hadis ke alfaz ibne-Bishr ki tarah (ye ( hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mani ( khud ( dhotey they jabke ibne-Mubarak aur abdul-Wahid ki hadis mein is tarah hai ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main usey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se dhoti thi."
674,"Abdullah-bin Shahab Kholani se riwayat hai, kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka mehman tha, mujhey apne donon kapdon mein ehtilam ho gaya to maine wo donon pani mein dubo diye, mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki aik kaneez ne dekh liya aur unhein bata diya to unhon-ne meri taraf paigham bhijwaayaa aur farmaya : tu ney apne donon kapdon ke sath aisa kyon kiya? maine kaha : maine neend mein wo dekha jo soney wala apni neend mein dekhta hai. unhon-ne puchha : kya tumhen un donon ( kapdon ( mein kuchh nazar aaya? maine kaha : nahi. unhon-ne farmaya : agar tum kuchh dekhtey to usey dho daaltey. maine khud ko dekha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey se usko khushk haalat main apne naakhun se khurch rahi hun."
675,"Wakee ne bayan kya, hamein Hisham ne hadis sunai : aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Fatima (binte-munzir) ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne (apni aur Hisham donon ki daadii) Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai aur puchha : ham mein se kisi ke kapdey ko haiz ka khoon lag jata hai to wo uske barey mein kya karey? aap ne farmaya : usey khurch daaley, phir pani daal kar usey ragdey, phir is par pani baha de (dho ley), phir usmein Namaz padh ley."
676,"Yahya-bin-Abdullah-bin-Salim, Malik-bin-Anas aur Amr-bin-Haris teenon ne Hisham-bin-Urwa ki uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath yahi riwayat isi tarah bayan ki jis tarah Yahya-bin-Saeed ne bayan ki."
677,"Wakee ne bayan kya, (kaha : ( hamein Aamash ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Mujahid ko Taaus se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar 2 qabron par hua to aap ne farmaya : un donon ko azab ho raha hai aur kisi badi ghalati ki bina par azab nahi ho raha (jis se bachna dushwar hotaa.) unmein aik to chughal khorii karta tha aur doosra apne peshab se bchney ka ehtimaam nahi karta tha. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir aap ne aik taaza khajoor ki chhadi mangwai aur usko 2 hisson mein cheer diya, phir aik hissey us qabr par gaad diya aur doosra us (doosri qabr) par, phir aap ne farmaya : ummeed hai jab tak ye 2 tahniyaan sookheingii nahi, unka azab halka rahega."
678,"abdul-Wahid ne isi sanad se Sulaiman Aamash se uper zikr ki gaee hadis riwayat ki, siwaey iske ke kaha : aur doosra peshab (apne ke baghair) ki taraf se (bchney ka ehtimaam nahi kartaa.)"
